4c1eb9d9-f38d-41e6-aeed-76479e15d4cf	Managing Partner	Senior leadership role responsible for overall firm strategy, client relationship oversight, and business development direction. Serves as primary decision-maker for engagement pursuit, pricing strategy, and high-stakes client negotiations.\r\n\r\nKey Responsibilities: Strategic planning, major client relationship management, proposal pricing and approval, contract negotiation, partner-level business development, firm growth initiatives\r\n\r\nReports To: Board of Directors / Partners\r\n\r\nDirect Reports: Principal Consultant, Business Development Manager, Project Manager\r\nDecision Authority: Final approval on engagement pursuit (>$50K), pricing strategy for all proposals, contract terms and modifications, strategic partnership agreements, major operational changes\r\n\r\nCore Competencies: Executive presence with C-level clients, complex deal negotiation, strategic business planning, P&L management, team leadership and development\r\n\r\nTypical Interactions: Client executives, internal project teams, business development prospects, industry partners, professional service providers	b24177e6-5639-46a6-acec-def85fa4b319
